import React from 'react'
  import { MDXTag } from '@mdx-js/tag'
  

export default class MDXContent extends React.Component {
  constructor(props) {
    super(props)
    this.layout = null
  }
  render() {
    const { components, ...props } = this.props

    return <MDXTag
             name="wrapper"
             
             components={components}><MDXTag name="h1" components={components} props={{"id":"tips-and-tricks"}}>{`Tips and Tricks`}</MDXTag>
{/* TOC */}
<MDXTag name="ul" components={components}>
<MDXTag name="li" components={components} parentName="ul"><MDXTag name="a" components={components} parentName="li" props={{"href":"#tips-and-tricks"}}>{`Tips and Tricks`}</MDXTag><MDXTag name="ul" components={components} parentName="li">
<MDXTag name="li" components={components} parentName="ul"><MDXTag name="a" components={components} parentName="li" props={{"href":"#dealing-with-records"}}>{`Dealing with records`}</MDXTag></MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="li" components={components} parentName="ul"><MDXTag name="a" components={components} parentName="li" props={{"href":"#load-balancing"}}>{`Load balancing`}</MDXTag></MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="li" components={components} parentName="ul"><MDXTag name="a" components={components} parentName="li" props={{"href":"#ports"}}>{`Ports`}</MDXTag></MDXTag>
</MDXTag></MDXTag>
</MDXTag>
{/* /TOC */}
<MDXTag name="h2" components={components} props={{"id":"dealing-with-records"}}>{`Dealing with records`}</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="p" components={components}><MDXTag name="inlineCode" components={components} parentName="p">{`curl -I <domain>`}</MDXTag></MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="p" components={components}>{`Example response:`}</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="pre" components={components}><MDXTag name="code" components={components} parentName="pre" props={{}}>{`HTTP/1.1 301 Moved Permanently
x-amz-id-2: GhbglnY4TMT7NQy4HEFfBbrYo1L6OgepT1130/R80lZm6yDUCH8Ok
x-amz-request-id: C72E7BA4D7A6DEB8
Date: Thu, 31 Aug 2017 22:51:42 GMT
Location: https://www.domain.com/
Content-Length: 0
Server: AmazonS3
`}</MDXTag></MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="p" components={components}><MDXTag name="inlineCode" components={components} parentName="p">{`dig afxr gitgood.club`}</MDXTag>{` - gives back record data.`}</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="h2" components={components} props={{"id":"load-balancing"}}>{`Load balancing`}</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="p" components={components}><MDXTag name="inlineCode" components={components} parentName="p">{`ab -n 1000 -c 50 "https://staging.aemc.prescoapps.co/"`}</MDXTag>{` - test Load Balance with reqs
.`}</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="h2" components={components} props={{"id":"ports"}}>{`Ports`}</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="p" components={components}><MDXTag name="inlineCode" components={components} parentName="p">{`sudo lsof -i :3090`}</MDXTag>{` - what's using port 3090.`}</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="p" components={components}><MDXTag name="inlineCode" components={components} parentName="p">{`telnet redrooster.com.au 22`}</MDXTag>{` - Does the server at redrooster.com.au listen on port 22 (standard ssh port)?`}</MDXTag>
           </MDXTag>
  }
}
